===[[Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket]]===
{{main|Blaine (Genetic Apex 221)}}
Blaine makes an appearance as a {{TCG|Supporter}} card in [[Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket]]'s first expansion, {{TCGP|Genetic Apex}}. On the turn the player plays this card, attacks used by their {{TCGP|Ninetales}}, {{TCGP|Rapidash}}, or {{TCGP|Magmar}} do an additional 30 damage to their opponent's Active Pokémon.

